multisystem
systems 3
mission_name Multisystem Test
mission_desc Hunt an Imperial fleet across three star systems.
gametype objectives
player_team rebel
player_ship X/W
player_spawn 0 0 0

system 1
bg stars
player_spawn 0 0 0
navpoint "Jump to Hoth" 800 0 0 true 2

at 0:00
spawn rebel follow X/W "Red 2" at -50 80 0
spawn rebel follow X/W "Red 3" at -50 -80 0
spawn empire T/F "Alpha 1" at 600 200 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/F "Alpha 2" at 650 -150 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/F "Alpha 3" at 700 100 50 facing -1 0 0

at 0:03 while player alive
message Welcome to the Anoat system. An Imperial patrol has been spotted nearby.
wait 4
message Engage the TIE Fighters, then jump to Hoth via the nav point. Press N to target, J to jump.
system 1

system 2
bg nebula
player_spawn 10000000 0 0
navpoint "Return to Anoat" 9999400 0 0 true 1
navpoint "Jump to Endor" 10000600 0 0 false 3 var endor_visible

on arrive while player alive
message Arriving in the Hoth system. Imperial ships detected.

at 0:00
spawn empire T/I "Beta 1" at 10000300 300 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/I "Beta 2" at 10000350 -200 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/I "Beta 3" at 10000250 100 100 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/I "Beta 4" at 10000400 -100 -50 facing -1 0 0
system 2

system 3
bg nebula2
player_spawn 20000000 0 0
navpoint "Return to Hoth" 19999400 0 0 true 2

on arrive while player alive
message The Endor system. The Obliterator is here. Take it down!

at 0:00
spawn empire T/I "Gamma 1" at 20000400 300 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/I "Gamma 2" at 20000450 -200 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/I "Gamma 3" at 20000350 100 100 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/I "Gamma 4" at 20000500 -100 -50 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/F "Delta 1" at 20000300 400 100 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire T/F "Delta 2" at 20000350 -400 -100 facing -1 0 0
system 3

at 0:00
spawn empire objective COR "Carnivore" at 10000500 600 0 facing -1 0 0
spawn empire objective ISD "Obliterator" at 20000600 800 0 facing -1 0 0

on destroyed empire_ship if ( name "Carnivore" )
endor_visible true
wait 2
message The Carnivore is down! Intel shows the Obliterator is at Endor. Jump point is now available.

when ( no empire objectives alive ) and ( players alive )
wait 3
victory

on victory
wait 2
message All Imperial objectives destroyed. Well done, pilot.

on defeat
wait 1
message Mission failed. The Empire tightens its grip on the sector.
